  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">William Lloyd Garrison sympathizes with David Lee Child and Lydia Maria Child in their suffering from &quot;unjust prosecution.&quot; He wants David Lee Child to be the editor of the Emancipator instead of Amos Augustus Phelps. David Lee Child&apos;s knowledge of politics is needed. There was an uproar in Boston over the kidnapping of two colored women.</subfield>
